Makes around 80 wontons

Ingredients:
700g prawn meat
100g ground pork shoulder (fatty)
50g leaf lard
80g dried shrimps (no head, or shells) - blended in thermomix till it's powder, speed 9/30seconds
50g dried flouder powder
100ml ginger scallion water (100ml water, 2 stalks of spring onion, a thumb of ginger, blended and then strained for the water)
70g scallions finely chopped
25g egg white
10g sugar
20g cornstarch
2g ground white pepper
10ml shaoxing wine
7.5g salt
10ml light soy sauce

Sesame oil purposely omitted. 
